data.description: Welcome home to this spacious 3 bedroom/2 full bath home. Functional layout with tons of windows for natural light. Enter the brick entry foyer that leads to the spacious great room with a wood burning fireplace. Large kitchen with built-in desk, breakfast nook, pantry and a good sized laundry room. The primary suite includes a spacious walk-in closet, linen closet, and master bath with double vanities. The two remaining bedrooms are also good sized. Guest bathroom also has double vanities. Enjoy sitting under the covered back porch overlooking the fully fenced backyard. Conveniently located to the interstate, shopping malls and entertainment. Schedule today for a private tour.
